                    </div>
                    <span>This book is focused on "Introduction to Game Design" and uses the C# language and DirectX 9 technology to illustrate the samples.<p>This book does not teach C# nor does it provide sufficient DirectX programming concepts.<p>If you are looking for a book that provides a good overview of how a 3D Game Engine works from the developer-perspective then this book is for you.<p>For those looking for a pre-built game engine upon which to learn then I suggest that you look somewhere else.</span>
                  
